title: Ultra Luxury! Lakeside Leisure, Boutique-Style Community, Balcony!
posting_body: ['Where Lake Life and City Living Are One In The Same!', 'Uptown, Minneapolis, MN', '$1595 per month', '1 Bedroom, 1 bath', '883 sq.', 'ft.', 'Lease Term: 12 Months', 'Parking: $125/Monthly', 'Uptown Energy.', 'Lakeside', 'Leisure...where lake life and city living are one and the same.', 'Our 45-unit, 6-floor boutique-style apartment complex is situated near Lake Calhoun and Calhoun Square in the heart of the thriving Uptown neighborhood in Minneapolis.', 'Stylish residences outfitted with contemporary amenities and open living spaces make this a sophisticated setting to socialize and unwind.', "Whether you choose to grill out on the terrace or enjoy the view from your private balcony, our diverse selection of 28 unique floor plans means that no matter what your lifestyle, you'll find a fit here.", 'With a top tier fitness center in the building, grocery stores and coffee shops just steps outside your front door, and underground parking availability, we make the urban Twin Cities living convenient and comfortable.', 'Community Amenities', 'Outdoor patio,', 'City and lake views,', 'Top tier fitness center,', 'Dog Wash,', '100% smoke free,', 'Secure Bicycle Parking,', 'Wi-Fi in common areas,', 'Club Room,', 'Heated underground parking,', 'Bicycle repair station,', 'Pet friendly,', '24-hour emergency maintenance,', 'Trash, Recycling & Composting.', 'Apartment Amenities*', 'Private balcony,', 'Stainless steel appliances,', 'Ceiling Fans,', 'Walk-in closets,', 'Expansive windows,', 'High-Speed Internet,', 'Granite countertops,', 'Kitchen islands,', 'Full-size washer and dryer,', 'Dishwasher and garbage disposal,', 'High Ceilings*.', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Prices and availability are subject to change.', 'Contact Us:', 'Apartment Resource', 'Toni Hill', 'show contact info']
